               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction&#xD;
- Mäqdǝmä Wängel “Introduction to the Gospels” (fols. 2r4ra-8rb)&#xD;
- Letter of Eusebius to Carpanius (fols. 8rb-8vb)&#xD;
- The “Synopsis of Classes” (fols. 8vb-9ra)&#xD;
- On the reliability of the Gospels (fols. 9ra-9vb)&#xD;
- Canon Tables (fols. 10va-14ra)&#xD;
II) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 14rb-58va)&#xD;
- List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Matthew: 70 titles (fols. 14rb-14va)&#xD;
- Bǝsratä Matewos “Gospel of Matthew” (fols. 15ra-58rb)&#xD;
- Postscript (fols. 58rb-58va)&#xD;
III) Gospel of Mark (fols. 58va-88ra)&#xD;
- Biography of Mark (fols. 58va-59ra)&#xD;
- List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Mark: 48 titles (fols. 59ra-59vb)&#xD;
- Bǝsratä Marqos “Gospel of Mark” (fols. 60ra-88ra)&#xD;
- Postscript (fol. 88ra)&#xD;
IV) Gospel of Luke (fols. 88rb-131ra)&#xD;
- List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Luke: 83 titles (fols. 88rb-88vb)&#xD;
- Bǝsratä Luqas “Gospel of Luke” (fols. 89ra-130vb)&#xD;
- Post-script (fols. 130vb-131ra)&#xD;
V) Gospel of John (fols. 131rb-163vb)&#xD;
- List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of John: 20 titles (fol. 131rb)&#xD;
- Bǝsratä Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols. 131ra-163va)&#xD;
- Postscript (fol. 163vb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-7; colophon.</summary>
